item.title: The edible wild mushroom
item.description: Schizophyllum alneum or Schizophyllum commune or tiny oyster mushrooms are edible wild mushroom. Schizophyllum is well known as split gill mushroooms, kanglayen in India, khurakding in Philippines, het bee in Thailand and jamur grigit in Indonesian.
